              </li>

              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-neutral-800">
                <Icon name="ph:check-circle-fill" class="w-5 h-5" />
                <span class="text-neutral-600"><a class="text-primary-600 hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1" href="https://github.com/Panmoni/yapbay-www" target="_blank">yapbay-www (this website)</a></span>
              </li>

              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-neutral-800">
                <Icon name="ph:check-circle-fill" class="w-5 h-5" />
                <span class="text-neutral-600"><a class="text-primary-600 hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1" href="https://github.com/Panmoni/yapbay-contracts-sui" target="_blank">yapbay-contracts-sui (move contracts)</a></span>
