                <span class="text-neutral-600"><a class="text-primary-600 hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1" href="https://github.com/Panmoni/yapbay-contracts" target="_blank">yapbay-contracts (gen1 Solidity contracts, obsolete for now)</a></span>
